      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 28 judgment</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 28 judgment</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>大過，棟橈，利有攸往，亨。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Da Guo suggests to us a beam that is weak. There will be advantage in moving (under its conditions) in any direction whatever; there will be success.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
