      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初六：藉用白茅，无咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first SIX, divided, shows one placing mats of the white m?o grass under things set on the ground. There will be no error.</seg>
