      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九二：枯楊生稊，老夫得其女妻，无不利。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second NINE, undivided, shows a decayed willow producing shoots, or an old husband in possession of his young wife. There will be advantage in every way.</seg>
